## Overview
The component provides a comprehensive interface for file processing. This documentation covers version 2.0.

## Authentication

**Parameters:**

- `offset` (integer): Starting position

|------|-------------|
| 400  | Bad Request |
| 401  | Unauthorized |
| 404  | Not Found |
